{"tid":226470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禾輋邨5人激戰　Tony Jaa飛入戰圈","createTime":"2017-05-02T14:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T14:39:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21af7733f94c9692cd4a05592ba89ab65401738d","tid":226470,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:06:01.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】沙田禾輋邨熟食中心，前晚有5名男子發生激烈爭執後大打出手，在三戰二之下，一名男子頭部受傷倒地，警方接報到場將傷者送院治理，涉案人士則已逃去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bRYf52PF-CI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbRYf52PF-CI&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=02165b82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bRYf52PF-CI</a>"},{"pid":"2b124762543ee9ec46f8a798ea24903015a4099a","tid":226470,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7531823f2b50e6b3d4356ce640129868a8b1093a","tid":226470,"uid":67660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f169cd69b5b523ce7227334f25bbc71b590a8049","tid":226470,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"日本人眼中的香港<br />\n<br />\n我叫池下遼十，是日本東京「新香港研究社」的社長兼副社長兼唯一社-員。<br />\n自小我便對「香港」抱著極大興趣，<br />\n<br />\n而從動畫； GAME 和漫畫當中，我對這個城市有著更深刻的了解。<br />\n綜合多套動畫和漫畫作品的描述，我得出以下幾項重點：<br />\n<br />\n１．<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人分成風水師、拳法家和黑社會三大類。</span><br />\n２．九龍（尤指九龍城寨）是個危險的地方。<br />\n３．香港的少林寺位於南方一個離島上。<br />\n４．香港擁有巨大的超級機械人。"},{"pid":"232d3d8e9f99728231150e7badb684d1e844b683","tid":226470,"uid":28590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"坐定定食住飯睇戲<img src=\"